    How gift orders work

  • Gift messages are added at checkout and shared with the Everyday Market Partner to include with your order.
  • One gift message per order, only available for select products and online orders.
  • Inappropriate or offensive messages will not be printed.
  • You can send your Everyday Market order to an alternate address if you have groceries in your cart.
  • Invoices (gift receipts) are not included in the delivery of your gift order.
  • Gift hampers, and items containing food, are not eligible for a change of mind refund under our Returns Policy
  • For orders containing liquor, a person over 18 must accept it. Photo ID to be shown on delivery.
  • Items are not gift wrapped.

    • Sending gifts to a different address? Multiple orders must be made.
